---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import GridBackground from '../../components/GridBackground.astro';
import ThemeToggle from '../../components/ThemeToggle.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="Outbound B2B — Asesoría 1:1 o gestionado por nosotros | TOF" description="Dos formas de hacer prospección B2B con The Outbound Force: que te enseñemos a hacerlo (asesoría 1:1) o que lo hagamos por vos (outbound gestionado).">

<GridBackground />

<nav id="navbar">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/web/" class="nav-logo">The Outbound <span>Force</span></a>
    <div class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
      <a href="/web/">Inicio</a>
      <a href="/web/outbound" class="nav-active">Outbound</a>
      <a href="/web/desarrollo-web">Desarrollo Web</a>
      <a href="/web/faq">FAQ</a>
      <a href="/web/contacto">Contacto</a>
      <ThemeToggle />
      <a href="https://calendar.app.google/Jxg7er6LkiL6tGEw6" class="nav-cta magnetic-btn" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Agendar Reunión</a>
    </div>
    <button aria-label="Menú" class="menu-toggle" id="menuToggle"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button>
  </div>
</nav>

<main id="main-content" tabindex="-1">
  <div style="height: 4.5rem;"></div>

  <section class="ch-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="ch-kicker">Outbound</span>
      <h1 class="ch-title">¿Cómo querés <em>generar tu demanda</em>?</h1>
      <p class="ch-desc">Dos caminos para construir un sistema de prospección B2B que llene tu agenda con clientes calificados. Elegí el que se adapta a tu momento.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ch-options">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ch-grid">

        <!-- OPTION 1: ASESORÍA -->
        <a href="/web/asesoria" class="ch-card ch-card-asesoria">
          <div class="ch-card-head">
            <div class="ch-icon">
              <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="ch-pill">Te enseñamos</span>
          </div>

          <h2 class="ch-card-title">Asesoría 1:1</h2>
          <p class="ch-card-tagline">Aprendés a hacer outbound vos mismo, con nuestro sistema completo.</p>

          <ul class="ch-bullets">
            <li>Clases individuales adaptadas a tu negocio</li>
            <li>Plantillas, scripts y SOPs probados</li>
            <li>Salís con tu propio sistema funcionando</li>
            <li>Ideal si querés autonomía y control</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="ch-meta">
            <span class="ch-meta-label">Para vos si...</span>
            <span class="ch-meta-text">querés dominar el proceso y construirlo internamente.</span>
          </div>

          <span class="ch-cta">
            Ver asesoría
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="16" height="16"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <!-- OPTION 2: GESTIONADO -->
        <a href="/web/outbound-gestionado" class="ch-card ch-card-gestionado">
          <span class="ch-badge">Más elegido</span>

          <div class="ch-card-head">
            <div class="ch-icon ch-icon-featured">
              <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2 3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="ch-pill ch-pill-featured">Lo hacemos por vos</span>
          </div>

          <h2 class="ch-card-title">Outbound gestionado</h2>
          <p class="ch-card-tagline">Profesionales ejecutan tu outbound de punta a punta. Vos recibís reuniones.</p>

          <ul class="ch-bullets">
            <li>LinkedIn + Email + Meta + Google gestionado</li>
            <li>+500 reuniones agendadas en 24 meses</li>
            <li>Reportes semanales y dashboard en vivo</li>
            <li>Cero curva de aprendizaje, máxima velocidad</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="ch-meta">
            <span class="ch-meta-label">Para vos si...</span>
            <span class="ch-meta-text">necesitás reuniones ya y querés delegar el proceso.</span>
          </div>

          <span class="ch-cta ch-cta-featured">
            Ver outbound gestionado
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="16" height="16"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </span>
        </a>

      </div>

      <p class="ch-footnote">¿No estás seguro cuál te conviene? <a href="https://calendar.app.google/Jxg7er6LkiL6tGEw6" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Agendá una llamada de 30 min</a> y lo definimos juntos.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<Footer />

</Layout>

<style is:global>
/* ═══ CHOOSER PAGE — light/dark adaptive ═══ */

.ch-hero {
  padding: 4rem 0 1rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.ch-kicker {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--font-b);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  color: var(--accent);
  background: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.08);
  padding: 0.4rem 0.85rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.ch-title {
  font-family: var(--font-d);
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  line-height: 1.05;
  color: var(--text);
  letter-spacing: -1.5px;
  margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
  max-width: 720px;
}
.ch-title em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); }
.ch-desc {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--text2);
  max-width: 560px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.ch-options { padding: 4rem 0 6rem; }
.ch-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  align-items: stretch;
}

.ch-card {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  padding: 2.5rem 2.25rem 2.25rem;
  border-radius: 24px;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--text);
  transition: all 0.4s var(--ease);
  overflow: hidden;
  isolation: isolate;
  min-height: 540px;
}

/* Asesoría card — clean white in light, subtle dark in dark */
.ch-card-asesoria {
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
}
.ch-card-asesoria::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(500px 300px at 50% 0%, rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.05), transparent 70%);
  z-index: -1;
}
.ch-card-asesoria:hover {
  border-color: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.35);
  transform: translateY(-6px);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.1);
}

/* Gestionado card — always dark gradient (featured) */
.ch-card-gestionado {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #2a1f3d 0%, #1a1625 100%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.3);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.18);
  color: #fff;
}
.ch-card-gestionado::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(700px 400px at 50% 0%, rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.20), transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(400px 300px at 100% 100%, rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.18), transparent 70%);
  z-index: -1;
}
.ch-card-gestionado:hover {
  border-color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.5);
  transform: translateY(-10px);
  box-shadow: 0 24px 48px rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.3);
}

.ch-badge {
  position: absolute;
  top: 1.5rem;
  right: 1.5rem;
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.4rem;
  font-family: var(--font-b);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  color: #fff;
  background: var(--accent);
  padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.4);
}
.ch-badge::before {
  content: "";
  width: 6px; height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: #fff;
  animation: pulse 2s infinite;
}

.ch-card-head {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.85rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
}

/* Asesoría icon (light card) */
.ch-card-asesoria .ch-icon {
  width: 56px; height: 56px;
  background: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.08);
  color: var(--accent);
  border-radius: 14px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
/* Gestionado icon (dark card) */
.ch-card-gestionado .ch-icon-featured {
  width: 56px; height: 56px;
  background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.22);
  color: #c4b5fd;
  border-radius: 14px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.ch-pill {
  font-family: var(--font-b);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.4px;
  color: var(--textm);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.ch-pill-featured { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75); }

.ch-card-title {
  font-family: var(--font-d);
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: 1.85rem;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -0.6px;
  margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
}
.ch-card-asesoria .ch-card-title { color: var(--text); }
.ch-card-gestionado .ch-card-title { color: #fff; }

.ch-card-tagline {
  font-size: 1.02rem;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
}
.ch-card-asesoria .ch-card-tagline { color: var(--text2); }
.ch-card-gestionado .ch-card-tagline { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); }

.ch-bullets {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.65rem;
  flex: 1;
}
.ch-bullets li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 0.65rem;
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.ch-card-asesoria .ch-bullets li { color: var(--text2); }
.ch-card-gestionado .ch-bullets li { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72); }

.ch-bullets li::before {
  content: "";
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 18px; height: 18px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background-size: 11px;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: center;
  margin-top: 1px;
}
.ch-card-asesoria .ch-bullets li::before {
  background: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.10);
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='%236d28d9' stroke-width='3' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'><polyline points='20 6 9 17 4 12'/></svg>");
  background-size: 11px;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: center;
}
.ch-card-gestionado .ch-bullets li::before {
  background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.18);
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='%23c4b5fd' stroke-width='3' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'><polyline points='20 6 9 17 4 12'/></svg>");
  background-size: 11px;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: center;
}

.ch-meta {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.25rem;
  padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
  border-radius: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
}
.ch-card-asesoria .ch-meta {
  background: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.04);
  border: 1px solid rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.10);
}
.ch-card-gestionado .ch-meta {
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  border: 1px solid rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.12);
}
.ch-meta-label {
  font-family: var(--font-b);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.6px;
  color: var(--accent);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.ch-card-gestionado .ch-meta-label { color: #a78bfa; }
.ch-meta-text {
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  line-height: 1.45;
}
.ch-card-asesoria .ch-meta-text { color: var(--text2); }
.ch-card-gestionado .ch-meta-text { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); }

.ch-cta {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  font-family: var(--font-b);
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  padding: 0.85rem 1.5rem;
  border-radius: 10px;
  margin-top: auto;
  transition: all 0.25s var(--ease);
}
.ch-card-asesoria .ch-cta {
  color: var(--accent);
  background: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.08);
  border: 1px solid rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.2);
}
.ch-card-asesoria:hover .ch-cta {
  background: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.15);
  border-color: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.4);
}
.ch-cta svg { transition: transform 0.25s var(--ease); }
.ch-card:hover .ch-cta svg { transform: translateX(4px); }

.ch-cta-featured {
  background: var(--accent);
  border: 1px solid var(--accent);
  color: #fff;
}
.ch-card-gestionado:hover .ch-cta-featured {
  background: #7c3aed;
  border-color: #7c3aed;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.4);
}

.ch-footnote {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 3rem;
  color: var(--text2);
  font-size: 0.95rem;
}
.ch-footnote a {
  color: var(--accent);
  text-decoration: underline;
  text-decoration-color: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.4);
  text-underline-offset: 3px;
  transition: all 0.2s var(--ease);
}
.ch-footnote a:hover {
  color: var(--accent-hover);
  text-decoration-color: var(--accent-hover);
}

/* ═══ Dark mode overrides ═══ */
body.dark .ch-card-asesoria {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025);
  border-color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.18);
}
body.dark .ch-card-asesoria:hover {
  border-color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.45);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}
body.dark .ch-card-asesoria .ch-icon {
  background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.10);
  color: #a78bfa;
}
body.dark .ch-pill { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55); }
body.dark .ch-card-asesoria .ch-card-title { color: #fff; }
body.dark .ch-card-asesoria .ch-card-tagline { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); }
body.dark .ch-card-asesoria .ch-bullets li { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72); }
body.dark .ch-card-asesoria .ch-bullets li::before {
  background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.18);
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='%23c4b5fd' stroke-width='3' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'><polyline points='20 6 9 17 4 12'/></svg>");
  background-size: 11px;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: center;
}
body.dark .ch-card-asesoria .ch-meta {
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  border-color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.12);
}
body.dark .ch-card-asesoria .ch-meta-label { color: #a78bfa; }
body.dark .ch-card-asesoria .ch-meta-text { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); }
body.dark .ch-card-asesoria .ch-cta {
  color: #fff;
  background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.12);
  border-color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.3);
}
body.dark .ch-card-asesoria:hover .ch-cta {
  background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.20);
  border-color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.5);
}
body.dark .ch-footnote { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55); }
body.dark .ch-footnote a { color: #a78bfa; text-decoration-color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.4); }
body.dark .ch-footnote a:hover { color: #c4b5fd; text-decoration-color: #c4b5fd; }
body.dark .ch-kicker { color: #a78bfa; background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.12); }
body.dark .ch-title { color: #fff; }
body.dark .ch-title em { color: #a78bfa; }
body.dark .ch-desc { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65); }

@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .ch-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .ch-card { min-height: auto; padding: 2rem 1.75rem; }
  .ch-card-gestionado { order: -1; }
  .ch-card-title { font-size: 1.55rem; }
  .ch-options { padding: 2.5rem 0 4rem; }
  .ch-hero { padding: 2.5rem 0 1rem; }
}
</style>

<script is:inline>
  window.addEventListener("scroll", function() {
    document.getElementById("navbar").classList.toggle("scrolled", window.scrollY > 50);
  });
  document.getElementById("menuToggle").addEventListener("click", function() {
    document.getElementById("navLinks").classList.toggle("open");
  });

  document.querySelectorAll('.magnetic-btn').forEach(function(btn) {
    var strength = 0.3;
    btn.addEventListener('mousemove', function(e) {
      var rect = btn.getBoundingClientRect();
      btn.style.transform = 'translate(' + (e.clientX - rect.left - rect.width / 2) * strength + 'px, ' + (e.clientY - rect.top - rect.height / 2) * strength + 'px)';
    });
    btn.addEventListener('mouseleave', function() {
      btn.style.transform = 'translate(0, 0)';
      btn.style.transition = 'transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)';
      setTimeout(function() { btn.style.transition = ''; }, 400);
    });
    btn.addEventListener('mouseenter', function() { btn.style.transition = 'none'; });
  });
</script>
